2016-02-02 : Version 1.2.0
--------------------------

* New drawing modes : lines and empty ellipses
* New build phase : walls & floors
* Shortcut to hide the starting point of the design (blinking X)
* Bug fixes


2016-01-26 : Version 1.1.2
--------------------------

* Bug fixes


2016-01-21 : Version 1.1.1 (unreleased)
---------------------------------------

* Bug fixes


2014-09-29 : Version 1.1.0 (unreleased)
---------------------------------------

* Undo / Redo support
* Cut / Copy / Paste support
* Help window
* New file action
* Confirmations before quitting / loading if a blueprint is modified
* New boolean preferences : ghost, crosshairs
* Protect mode : allows to use the 'dig' mode only on walls, thus not clearing stairs, holes and ramps


